description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a GP to join Hamdon Medical Centre in South Somerset, where you will have the opportunity to work with a dynamic, patient focused and enthusiastic team helping to further develop the best enhanced primary care and patient service in the country. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hamdon Medical Centre is part of Symphony Healthcare Services Ltd (&quot;SHS&quot;), a primary care organisation established as part of the award winning Symphony Programme Vanguard developing new models of care. With a growing network of 14 practices and 40 employed GPs in Somerset, we are now recruiting for 5 GP sessions at Hamdon. The successful candidate will join the team working two sessions on a Monday,t wo on Tuesday and one on Wednesday.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hamdon Medical Centre is an innovative practice:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Semi-rural practice in a village location&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implementing enhanced primary care models of service delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team includes health coaches and medicines management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Circa 5,000 patients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;purpose built premises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;EMIS Web practice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CQC inspection 2019 rated the practice as &quot;Good&quot; in all areas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We offer our GPs a range of flexible working options together with a competitive remuneration package based on the BMA GP contract with additional incentive payments and further allowances for GPs with specialist skills and experience. Tier 2 Visa sponsorship available.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For more information or to arrange an informal visit, please contact Luena Eeles (Practice Manager) on &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;l.eeles@nhs.net &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;or 01935 822236.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
